    <div class="example" id="switch">
      <h2><a href="./">Go в примери</a>: Превключване (Switch)</h2>
      
      <table>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>Изявленията от вида <em>switch</em> (превключване) изразяват
условия с множество разклонения.</p>

          </td>
          <td class="code empty leading">
            
          
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            
          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            <a href="https://go.dev/play/p/bYuT5zZYXYz"><img title="Run code" src="play.png" class="run" /></a><img title="Copy code" src="clipboard.png" class="copy" />
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kn">package</span> <span class="nx">main</span></span></span></code></pre>
